      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        d-vun-mag-val-uni    =    zero
                     move  "#"            to   w-prn-liv-flg-val
                     go to prn-liv-det-440.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Altrimenti : a sommatoria valore    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-410.
       prn-liv-det-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se valorizzazione al costo ultimo       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Richiamo modulo di magazzino        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "VM"                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-ope      .
           move      0002                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-val      .
           move      rr-dat-val           to   d-vun-mag-dat-val      .
           move      03                   to   d-vun-mag-tip-mag      .
           move      rf-dpm-num-map       to   d-vun-mag-num-mag      .
           move      "pgm/mag/prg/obj/pmag300v"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using d-vun-mag              .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se esito operazione negativo si     *
      *                          * prova con la valorizzazione a costo *
      *                          * standard                            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        d-vun-mag-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-liv-det-405.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se valore determinato pari a zero : *
      *                          * si pone in On il flag di determi-   *
      *                          * nazione non eseguibile e si va' a   *
      *                          * fine determinazione valore unitario *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        d-vun-mag-val-uni    =    zero
                     move  "#"            to   w-prn-liv-flg-val
                     go to prn-liv-det-440.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Altrimenti : a sommatoria valore    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-410.
       prn-liv-det-405.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se valorizzazione al costo standard     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Richiamo modulo di magazzino        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "VM"                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-ope      .
           move      0003                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-val      .
           move      rr-dat-val           to   d-vun-mag-dat-val      .
           move      03                   to   d-vun-mag-tip-mag      .
           move      rf-dpm-num-map       to   d-vun-mag-num-mag      .
           move      "pgm/mag/prg/obj/pmag300v"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using d-vun-mag              .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se valore determinato pari a zero : *
      *                          * si pone in On il flag di determi-   *
      *                          * nazione non eseguibile e si va' a   *
      *                          * fine determinazione valore unitario *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        d-vun-mag-val-uni    =    zero
                     move  "#"            to   w-prn-liv-flg-val
                     go to prn-liv-det-440.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Altrimenti : a sommatoria valore    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-410.
       prn-liv-det-410.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sommatoria valore                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione sub-valore parziale  *
      *                          * per l'elemento in esame             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      d-vun-mag-val-uni    to   w-prn-liv-det-sub      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Applicazione decimali gestione      *
      *                          * magazzino                           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           divide    100                  into w-prn-liv-det-sub      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Calcolo                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           multiply  w-esp-scl-dtp-qta    by   w-prn-liv-det-sub      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Sommatoria vera e propria           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           add       w-prn-liv-det-sub    to   w-prn-liv-det-val      .
       prn-liv-det-415.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo su scansione distinta base      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-240.
       prn-liv-det-420.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se subdistinta virtuale                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       prn-liv-det-425.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si entra nel livello successivo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-240.
       prn-liv-det-440.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Fine scansione e determinazione                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       prn-liv-det-445.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A stampa vera e propria                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-800.
       prn-liv-det-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa vera e propria                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       prn-liv-det-820.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
