      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        p-res                >    1
                     go to prn-liv-det-840.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Intestazione pagina                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   int-pag-sta-000      thru int-pag-sta-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
